{"tid":851162,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同男朋友去完鬼屋終於睇清佢份人!","createTime":"2018-10-07T02:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T08:00:30.000Z","uid":34252,"like":6,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9b4f809cce7afd62948650fc8ab60db16419ac2f","tid":851162,"uid":34252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T02:37:44.000Z","msg":"同男朋友去完OP個哈囉喂,但我真係勁嬲&hellip;<br />\n正常入鬼屋呀,女朋友驚男朋友都會捉實佢啦,<br />\n但入去玩鬼屋果時,我已經一路行一路縮緊,<br />\n佢仲要行行下推我出去,搵我做擋箭牌<br />\n我果下嬲到真係想喊,<br />\n又驚又嬲咁焗住行完全程,到出口先爆佢<br />\n點知佢道完歉話,咁我真係驚呀ma<br />\n<br />\n聽完我仲嬲!咁既男人姐係話佢會係我有難果陣推我出去啦,自己驚就推我出去,<br />\n而家佢反而話我小氣嬲咁耐&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597bb73cb0967cd7aff44a5dab1001c312700d73","tid":851162,"uid":123456,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T02:43:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抵啦 臭雞<br />\n雞就係要比人利用㗎啦</span>"},{"pid":"230c380bc71a118364c11b3a2b66317e02271b48","tid":851162,"uid":167102,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T02:43:17.000Z","msg":"條仔咁廢飛得啦，見到樓主個樣都唔驚驚鬼屋啲特技化妝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f38426f7b31c8bdbf589fb49c8b0f0743da7657","tid":851162,"uid":2547,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T02:43:43.000Z","msg":"呢d男人真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d31beee116a00783115aca7fbe9c9972b29ece","tid":851162,"uid":64948,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T02:44:55.000Z","msg":"兩個男人去玩就咪咁計較啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a3fc5610819c568fa09fd29c1092cb0d74d5c7f","tid":851162,"uid":189336,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T02:53:21.000Z